 <span data-ttu-id="ecfe9-119">Diese Eigenschaft verweist auf die Position am Anfang des dem erkannten Ausdruck in das Eingabegerät generierten Audiostream.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ecfe9-119">This property references the position at the beginning of the recognized phrase in the input device's generated audio stream.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ecfe9-120">Im Gegensatz dazu, die `RecognizerAudioPosition` Eigenschaft von der <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine> und <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognizer> Klassen verweisen, die Erkennung Position innerhalb der Audioeingabe.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ecfe9-120">By contrast, the `RecognizerAudioPosition` property of the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine> and <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognizer> classes reference the recognizer's position within its audio input.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ecfe9-121">Diese Positionen können unterschiedlich sein.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ecfe9-121">These positions can be different.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ecfe9-122">Weitere Informationen finden Sie unter [mit Spracherkennung Recognition Ereignissen](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/01c598ca-2e0e-4e89-b303-cd1cef9e8482).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ecfe9-122">For more information, see [Using Speech Recognition Events](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/01c598ca-2e0e-4e89-b303-cd1cef9e8482).</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="ecfe9-123">Die <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.RecognizedAudio.StartTime%2A> -Eigenschaft ruft die Systemzeit zu Beginn der Erkennungsvorgang ab.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ecfe9-123">The <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.RecognizedAudio.StartTime%2A> property gets the system time at the start of the recognition operation.</span></span>  
  
   
  
